        <div class="jumbotron text-center" style="background-color: yellow;" id="head">
            <h1>Thank you for registering with us!!</h1>
            <h2>click here to view our instructions of the ideathon before you proceed</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="jumbotron" style="background-image:linear-gradient(to bottom,blue,grey);color: white;">
          <h2>The allotted problem statement for your team name is as given below:</h2>
          <h3><%=ques%></h3>
        </div>
        <div class="announcements" style="font-family: 'Franklin Gothic Medium', 'Arial Narrow', Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;">
          <div class="jumbotron text-center">
            <h2>Recent Announcements</h2>
          </div>
          <div id="chat-window" style="background-color: bisque; height: 40%;">
            
          </div>
          <input type="text" id="secret" placeholder="Enter the secret key to make announcements,this is only for admins" style="width: 100%; text-align: center;">
          <input type="text" id="handle" placeholder="Enter your name" style="width: 100%;text-align: center;">
          <input type="text" id="message" placeholder="Enter the message" style="width: 100%;text-align: center;">
          <button class="btn  btn-primary" style="margin-top: 2%;margin-bottom: 2%;" id="btn">Send</button>
        </div>
        <script>
          var socket=io.connect();
          var chat=document.getElementById('chat-window');
          var handle=document.getElementById('handle');
          var message=document.getElementById('message');
          var btn=document.getElementById('btn');
          var secret=document.getElementById('secret');
          btn.addEventListener('click',function(){
           if(secret.value=='21468034')
           {
            socket.emit('chat',{
              message:message.value,
              handle:handle.value
            });
           }
          })
          socket.on('chat',function(data){
            chat.innerHTML+='<p><strong>' +data.handle+ ':</strong>'+data.message+'</p>';
          })


        </script>
        <div class="instructions">
            <ul>
                <li>
                   Accurate drive link for the project must be shared.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Creation of multiple accounts is prohibited.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Every participant is allowed to submit only a single idea.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Any file format is accepted, but PDF would be appreciable.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Ideas will be strictly inspected for plagiarism, if positive then all the related ideas will be disqualified.
                </li>
                <li>
                    The participants should strictly follow the idea that is allotted to them by the portal,any changes would lead to disqualification.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Timings for the ideathon will be from 9:00am to 9:00pm forth which any ideas will be not accepted.
                </li>
                <li>
                    All the selected people will recieve an email and will be promoted to the next round.
                </li>
                <li>
                    Your file can be updated multiple times.
                </li>
                <li>
                  IEEE-RAS wishes you all the best!!
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <style>
            .instructions{
